Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.08,0:03:11.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}風學姐 姿勢自然點就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.32,0:03:12.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}只是下意識啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.02,0:03:15.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}話說你最近很熱衷攝影啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.00,0:03:18.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}學姐快要畢業了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.70,0:03:21.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}留下社員們的活動紀錄是很重要的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.91,0:03:26.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不過我就算畢業 也會常來這裡的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.68,0:03:28.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}還要待在這裡啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.36,0:03:30.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我就猜到你會這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.87,0:03:33.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嘴上這麼說其實很高興吧 夏凜
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.73,0:03:38.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你這是什麼反應
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.17,0:03:41.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}看著她們就湧起我的創作慾啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.44,0:03:42.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你也覺得吧 桑喬
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.62,0:03:44.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.88,0:03:46.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這孩子能說話嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.20,0:03:49.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}風風學姐和小魚乾給我好多靈感
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.77,0:03:51.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我回去就以她們為原型寫本書
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.01,0:03:52.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}等…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.89,0:03:54.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}再見
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.42,0:03:56.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}明天見
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.31,0:03:57.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}再見 園園
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.62,0:03:59.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}給我等等
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.98,0:04:06.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}對了 畢業旅行去哪裡好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.17,0:04:08.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}年末的時候哪裡都沒去成
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.86,0:04:12.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}就是啊 用大赦的公費一起去泡溫泉怎樣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.39,0:04:17.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我之前去泡過溫泉 能換個地方嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.03,0:04:18.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}登山也很不錯嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.81,0:04:19.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}登山？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.04,0:04:26.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}迷路的小貓咪 你在哪裡呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.23,0:04:29.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}找不到啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.60,0:04:32.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}對了樹 用貓語叫牠出來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.02,0:04:36.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}喵～喵～喵
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.30,0:04:38.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}再…再野性一點
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.06,0:04:40.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}真棒 寸寸真棒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.16,0:04:40.84,BackGround,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.84,0:04:42.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}請不要拍啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.90,0:04:44.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.71,0:04:48.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}過來 一起回家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.13,0:04:52.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}乖乖
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.67,0:04:54.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}友奈好眼力
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.84,0:04:57.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我嚇到牠了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.97,0:05:00.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}尋找小貓的委託完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.27,0:05:03.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}學姐 拍一張照留作紀念吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.41,0:05:04.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好耶
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.41,0:05:14.64,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}その先でまた会えるから
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.41,0:05:14.64,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}在漫長旅路的前方與你重逢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.64,0:05:16.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你們唱得真好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.57,0:05:18.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}配合也完美
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.84,0:05:20.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我們也來唱一首吧 友奈
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.50,0:05:24.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗯 等一下就寫作業
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.28,0:05:27.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}睡糊塗了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.16,0:05:30.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}小魚乾 我們一起唱個痛快吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.10,0:05:31.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.78,0:05:40.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}友奈
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.97,0:05:42.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}夏凜
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.80,0:05:45.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}能聊一下嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.90,0:05:48.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}聊什麼 夏凜
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.97,0:05:50.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}去走走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.40,0:05:58.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好久沒來這邊了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.23,0:06:02.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}上次救東鄉的時候來過而已吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.44,0:06:05.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}友奈 那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.88,0:06:08.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我能先問個問題嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.37,0:06:11.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}夏凜不冷嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.28,0:06:15.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}抱歉 我都沒考慮到
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.26,0:06:17.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}換個地方吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.58,0:06:19.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不要緊的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.15,0:06:21.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這樣就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.07,0:06:24.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好暖和
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.19,0:06:32.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}之前風說過 畢業後也會常來社團吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.27,0:06:32.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.65,0:06:37.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我聽她那麼說或許有點開心
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.10,0:06:39.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}有點？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.32,0:06:41.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}就一點啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.20,0:06:46.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但是…也還是很…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.99,0:06:48.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}很高興吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.08,0:06:52.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.39,0:07:01.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你看 我也學會把心裡話說出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.04,0:07:04.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}友奈也說出來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.51,0:07:08.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}年末這陣子 友奈你好奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.92,0:07:10.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}一定發生什麼了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.88,0:07:16.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我會幫助你的 能告訴我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.63,0:07:18.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}友奈
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.55,0:07:21.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}沒什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.51,0:07:26.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}沒關係的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.47,0:07:30.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不管是什麼煩惱 我都能接受
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.38,0:07:31.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我很在乎你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.68,0:07:33.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}夏凜
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.07,0:07:35.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我會幫你的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.73,0:07:38.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}只要是為了你 我什麼都願意做
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.24,0:07:42.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我好高興 有個朋友能讓我這麼想
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.45,0:07:47.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是友奈你們 讓我有這份心的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.16,0:07:49.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}夏凜
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.20,0:07:52.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}發生什麼事了 友奈
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.80,0:08:00.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那…那個
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.44,0:08:06.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}真的…沒什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.32,0:08:10.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.94,0:08:13.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}夏凜
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.69,0:08:19.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}勇者社不是…「有煩惱要跟大家說」嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.69,0:08:25.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我真的很想幫上朋友的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.17,0:08:30.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}夏凜 等一下 夏凜！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.94,0:08:51.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}對不起 對不起…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.28,0:09:07.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}友奈最近的樣子果然不太對勁
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.44,0:09:14.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是大吉耶 太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.20,0:09:17.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不對 抽到大吉的話
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.98,0:09:20.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}友奈會笑得更燦爛才對
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.41,0:09:25.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但為何她的表情看起來這麼難受
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.64,0:09:30.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}她肯定碰上什麼不好跟我們說的事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.45,0:09:31.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.73,0:09:36.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我來查明真相
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.50,0:09:42.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn華康鐵線龍門W3\bord0.2\blur5\shad3\3c&H304133&\4c&H35724F&\pos(320,605)}目標
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.25,0:09:42.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn華康鐵線龍門W3\bord0.2\blur5\shad3\3c&H304133&\4c&H35724F&\pos(475,605)}睡眠中
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.04,0:09:42.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn華康鐵線龍門W3\bord0.2\blur5\shad3\3c&H304133&\4c&H35724F&\pos(730,605)}可以入侵室內。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.71,0:09:46.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn華康鐵線龍門W3\bord0.2\blur5\shad3\3c&H120F07&\4c&H120F07&\pos(430,605)}收到。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.46,0:09:45.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn華康鐵線龍門W3\bord0.2\blur5\shad3\3c&H120F07&\4c&H120F07&\pos(625,605)}請原地待命。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.18,0:09:52.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn華康鐵線龍門W3\bord0.2\blur5\shad3\3c&H304133&\4c&H35724F&\pos(400,605)}開始入侵
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.30,0:09:52.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn華康鐵線龍門W3\bord0.2\blur5\shad3\3c&H304133&\4c&H35724F&\pos(700,605)}請打開鎖。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.68,0:09:53.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn華康鐵線龍門W3\bord0.2\blur5\shad3\3c&H304133&\4c&H35724F&\pos(530,605)}收到。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.75,0:10:11.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}友奈 燈都沒關就睡了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.65,0:10:14.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}抱歉 我偷偷進來了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.44,0:10:16.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}有線索嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.03,0:10:22.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那是！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.79,0:10:29.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}友奈剛上國中時 4月3日託父母買卻從未翻過的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.39,0:10:30.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這套叢書居然有一本凸了出來
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.99,0:10:41.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}勇者御記…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.03,0:10:44.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}為什麼裡面藏著這個
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.00,0:10:49.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}可能…不對 這裡面肯定有線索
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.74,0:10:51.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.80,0:11:08.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}友奈 對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.15,0:11:11.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我就借走了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.58,0:11:18.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這是友奈寫的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.26,0:11:22.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}友奈最近的樣子很奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.24,0:11:24.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}原因可能就寫在這裡面
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.25,0:11:28.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}居然還有這種東西
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.64,0:11:30.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我能插句話嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.67,0:11:31.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}園園？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.35,0:11:35.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我也擔心悠悠 就調查了一下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.33,0:11:38.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我最近不是比大家早回去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.61,0:11:41.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}其實是去大赦的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.16,0:11:43.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}大赦…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.73,0:11:48.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我先說結論 悠悠的樣子會不對勁
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.52,0:11:52.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}其實是因為受天神的神罰所苦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.80,0:11:55.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}園園 你是說…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.22,0:11:56.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}聽我說 鷲鷲
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.18,0:11:58.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}根據大赦的調查
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.73,0:12:02.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}如果悠悠把神罰說出來 寫下來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.14,0:12:04.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}神罰便會傳染
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.75,0:12:09.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}所以這本日記是非常危險的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.64,0:12:12.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你們還是要看嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.92,0:12:18.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}當然 我很擔心友奈啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.82,0:12:25.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那一起來看悠悠的御記吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.92,0:12:35.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}最開始是在年末
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.12,0:12:39.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}大赦的人發覺我情況有異 專程上門來找我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.12,0:12:43.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}他們透過神囑和研究 已經查明了情況
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.45,0:12:45.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}他們希望我能寫日記 留下神聖的記錄
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.05,0:12:48.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}便給了我這本御記
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.68,0:12:50.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我能堅持下去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.93,0:12:55.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}為什麼會變這樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.03,0:13:00.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我在大戰中受到了巨大的消耗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.37,0:13:03.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}全身幾乎散花殆盡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.25,0:13:07.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我甚至因為觸碰到了敵人的御魂
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.24,0:13:09.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}自己的靈魂也被御魂吸走了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.15,0:13:16.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}等我醒過來 那裡是我救東鄉的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.01,0:13:19.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是一片遼闊無垠的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.17,0:13:38.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我奮力掙扎 想要逃出這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.70,0:13:44.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這裡卻是那麼的寬廣 走也走不出去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.09,0:13:51.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}大家 救救我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.47,0:13:56.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}就算孤身一人 勇者也…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.48,0:14:01.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}勇者也不會放棄戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.84,0:14:02.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}東鄉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.97,0:14:04.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}只要信念還在
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.51,0:14:06.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}東鄉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.36,0:14:10.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}希望就不會消散…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.35,0:14:12.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}東鄉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.05,0:14:16.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}無論有任何代價 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.83,0:14:20.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}東鄉 東鄉 東鄉！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.61,0:14:27.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我 不希望 失去最寶貴的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.65,0:14:32.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}東鄉在哭啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.91,0:14:39.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我 我 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.04,0:14:41.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我是勇者
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.28,0:14:49.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}勇者不會對哭泣的朋友坐視不理
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.13,0:14:53.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}勇者就看毅力 我一定要回去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.95,0:15:08.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}藍烏鴉？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.46,0:15:31.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我想藍烏鴉是叫我跟牠走
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.24,0:15:40.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}所以我朝著光芒的方向不斷前行
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.69,0:15:43.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}於是我終於回到了這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.99,0:15:47.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但身體卻不一樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.99,0:15:50.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我和大家從散花狀態恢復了過來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.16,0:15:54.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但並非是獻上的祭品回到了我們身上
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.67,0:15:59.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}恢復的身體能力是神樹大人創造的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.62,0:16:04.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}花了很多時間 才成了我們自己身體的一部分
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.82,0:16:07.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}為了治癒強行盛開 最後散花的我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.95,0:16:11.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}神樹大人把我全身都變成了自己做的零件
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.90,0:16:16.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}大赦稱我為「御姿」
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.47,0:16:21.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}「御姿」說好聽點 是種非常神聖的存在
